snippet.title: This is EVE - Uncensored
snippet.description:
EVE Online is the massively multiplayer sci-fi universe that has captivated countless gamers' imaginations for over a decade. "This is EVE" takes you into the game using in-game footage and the voice comms of actual players. Battle cries, calls to action, cheers of victory, panicked escapes and virtual high-fives... This is EVE Online.

Note: This video contains strong language. 
Clean version: http://youtu.be/e2X1MIR1KMs

Start playing EVE for free now: http://trial.eveonline.com

Want to jump right in? Choose from our subscription offers at https://secure.eveonline.com/buy/
